    "en": {
      "title": "New faces for four positions in the House of Representatives",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Two Deputy Organizers and two Assistant Organizers of the ruling party in Parliament have also been appointed.",
        "According to the Prime Minister's Office, Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna MPs Mr. Sagara Kariyawasam and Mr. Jayantha Katagoda have been appointed as Deputy Organizers of the ruling party and Mr. Kokila Gunawardena and Mr. Madhura Withanage and Janaka Tissa Kuttiarachchi as Assistant Organizers.",
        "The appointment letters related to those positions were handed over to those MPs by Prime Minister Dinesh Gunawardena at the Prime Minister's Office yesterday (27).",
        "Minister of the House of Parliament Susil Premajayantha, Minister of the Chief Organizer of the Government Party Prasanna Ranatunga, Additional Secretary to the President and Secretary of the Chief Organizer of the Government Party Lawyer Chaminda Kularatne, Additional Secretary to the Prime Minister and Secretary of the Leader of the House Harsha Wijewardene also attended this event."
      ],
